<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وقَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٧ص٩٢:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الزُّهْرِيُّ:</span> لَا بَأسَ بِذَبِيحَةِ نَصَارَى العَرَبِ،<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَإِنْ سَمِعْتَهُ يُسَمِّي لِغَيْرِ اللهِ فَلَا تَأكُلْ،<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَإِنْ لَمْ تَسْمَعْهُ , فَقَدْ أَحَلَّهُ اللهُ لَكَ , وَعَلِمَ كُفْرَهُمْ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَيُذْكَرُ عَنْ عَلِيٍّ، نَحْوُهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَقَالَ الحَسَنُ ,<span class="c5"> وَإِبْرَاهِيمُ:</span> لَا بَأسَ بِذَبِيحَةِ الأَقْلَفِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>